data.title: Grand Haven Lighthouse
data.text:
Our mission is to preserve and restore Grand Haven’s Entrance and Inner Lighthouse structures along with any associated artifacts. Through public promotion and education, onsite interpretive displays and artifact presentations, the history and importance of the lighthouse structures will be conveyed to residents and visitors alike. The lighthouses in Grand Haven do more than guide Lake Michigan sailors.
